  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK244">
<l>maṉṉuyi rōmpi yaruḷāḷvāṟ killeṉpa</l>
<l>taṉṉuyi rañcum viṉai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(The wise) say that the evils, which his soul would dread, will never come upon the man who exercises kindness and protects the life (of other creatures)</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
